-- Thales, Germany's OHB May Sign Satellite Order This Month, Tribune Reports
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-09-22T05:15:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-22/thales-ohb-may-sign-1-7-billion-satellite-order-this-month-tribune-says.html
Thales SA and OHB Technology AG may
sign a weather-satellite contract worth 1.3 billion euros with
the European Space Agency at the end of September, La Tribune
reported, without citing anyone.  The partners would have to sub-contract 60 percent of the
value of the contract, according to the newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  